@startuml llm-cli-proxy-architecture
!include _standard-style.puml

title LLM Subscription Provider Architecture (@rapid/llm-proxy)\nDirect HTTP + CLI Shell-Out with Proxy Bridge

top to bottom direction

package "Docker Container (coding-services)" {
  component [Semantic Analysis\nMCP Server] as semantic <<core>>
  component [LLM Service\n(Provider Registry)] as llmservice <<core>>
  component [Copilot Provider\n(proxy mode)] as copilotprov <<agent>>
  component [Claude Code Provider\n(proxy mode)] as claudeprov <<agent>>
  component [Groq Provider] as groqprov <<api>>
  component [Anthropic Provider] as anthropicprov <<api>>

  llmservice -down-> copilotprov : priority 1
  llmservice -down-> groqprov : priority 2
  llmservice -down-> claudeprov : priority 3
  llmservice -down-> anthropicprov : priority 4
  semantic -down-> llmservice : LLM requests
}

rectangle "host.docker.internal" {
  package "Host: LLM Proxy Bridge (port 12435)" {
    component [llm-proxy.mjs\nExpress Server] as proxy <<api>>
    component [POST /api/complete] as complete <<api>>
    component [GET /health] as health <<api>>

    proxy -down-> complete
    proxy -down-> health
  }

  package "Host: Direct Copilot HTTP" {
    component [Direct HTTP POST\nto Copilot API] as copilothttp <<api>>
  }

  package "Host: Claude CLI" {
    component [claude -p\n--output-format json\n(Max OAuth)] as claudecli <<cli>>
  }

  complete -down-> copilothttp : copilot requests
  complete -down-> claudecli : claude-code requests
}

cloud "External APIs" {
  component [Copilot API\ncopilot-api.{enterprise}] as copilotapi <<external>>
  component [Anthropic API] as anthropicapi <<external>>
  component [Groq API] as groqapi <<external>>
}

database "Host Auth Stores" {
  component [~/.local/share/opencode/auth.json\nCopilot OAuth token] as copilotauth <<storage>>
  component [macOS Keychain\nClaude Max OAuth] as keychain <<storage>>
}

' Cross-boundary connections
copilotprov SYNC_LINE proxy : HTTP via\nhost.docker.internal:12435
claudeprov SYNC_LINE proxy : HTTP via\nhost.docker.internal:12435
groqprov ASYNC_LINE groqapi : HTTPS (direct)
anthropicprov ASYNC_LINE anthropicapi : HTTPS (direct)

' Host-side connections
copilothttp SYNC_LINE copilotapi : HTTPS POST\n/chat/completions
copilothttp <.. copilotauth : reads OAuth token\n(refresh every 60s)
claudecli <.. keychain : reads OAuth\n(managed by CLI)

note right of proxy
  **Split Routing**
  - Copilot: Direct HTTP POST (~2s)
    No SDK, no subprocess, no JSON-RPC
  - Claude: CLI shell-out (~12s)
    JSON output, exact token counts
    ANTHROPIC_API_KEY stripped from env
end note

note right of copilothttp
  **Copilot Auth**
  Bearer token from auth.json
  Enterprise: copilot-api.{host}
  Public: api.githubcopilot.com
end note

note right of claudecli
  **Claude Auth**
  Max OAuth from Keychain
  Cannot use OAuth directly
  against api.anthropic.com
  (server-side allowlisting)
end note

note bottom of llmservice
  **Provider Priority**
  1. copilot (proxy) — free, ~2s
  2. groq — API key, fast
  3. claude-code (proxy) — free, ~12s
  4. anthropic — API key
  5. openai — API key
  6. gemini — API key
  7. github-models — API key
end note

@enduml
